
Question
========
  
Which of the following variables is not a continuous variable?
  
Answerlist
----------
* The time needed to solve a math problem.
* Temperature.
* Weight.
* Number of children per family. 

Solution
========

Answerlist
----------
* Time is a continuous variable. 3.5 minutes or 6.93 seconds are possible values.
* Temperature is a continuous variable. It can be 13.5 degrees outside, or the oven can be 181.7 degrees hot. 
* Weight is a continuous variable. Someone can weigh 71.7 kilograms, or you can have 145.6 grams of sugar left in the bag.
* This answer is correct. We count the number of children. This is a discrete variable. 

